2.  <span data-ttu-id="57699-106">引发 <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.OnRowUpdating%2A> 事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="57699-106">The <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.OnRowUpdating%2A> event is raised.</span></span>  
  
3.  <span data-ttu-id="57699-107">该命令执行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="57699-107">The command executes.</span></span>  
  
4.  <span data-ttu-id="57699-108">如果该命令设置，则第一个返回的结果放入<xref:System.Data.DataRow>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="57699-108">If the command is set to FirstReturnedRecord, then the first returned result is placed in the <xref:System.Data.DataRow>.</span></span>  
  
